Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.01,0:00:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到无聊的视察终于要结束了 我就感觉很清静
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你还真会做表面功夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死囚乐园好也罢坏也罢 都是这个社会的缩影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是如实模仿社会系统所制造出的微型世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的音乐背后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有着不堪入目的争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让鲜血四溅的不就是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过是在提供而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给予这帮疯子宝贵的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:01:02.72,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Strict control of reason and reality
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.76,0:01:07.18,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Cut myself and scream for their insanity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:11.48,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Wake up into this nightmare that will never end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:16.28,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}The main attraction of this twisted master plan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.93,0:01:33.28,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I will be your deadman
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:37.66,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}With nothing but this blood on my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:42.10,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stuck in your Wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:46.43,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I wanna make you bleed just like me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:50.95,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}So make me your deadman
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:55.23,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}With only poison in my veins
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:01:59.64,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stuck in your Wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:01.95,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stuck in a battle I have to make
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:04.72,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm gonna make you bleed like me
