Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:11.36,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,505)\pos(994,532)}#12   救 济
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:11.36,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,505)\pos(1053,477)}Grateful Dead
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本那么温柔 那么强大的人却…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是那样 其实他很软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…没能保护好他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为自己能让他从这个世界逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 他杀了许多自己人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦角?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他很弱?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 只能沉默不语 或随之疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 为什么都还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做这种事情我也不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手吧 凪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想让丸太你来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快闪开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 这种程度白是不会痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那么弱 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋丸太 快闪开吧 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 凪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样 看着朋友被红衣男杀掉 渣到根了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 「没有时间去考虑复仇」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你对我说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前提是「只要还有希望」 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子…我的光芒 已经没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里只有黑暗 和憎恨!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 你会说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪的痛苦 其实我无法体会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是死了的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被杀掉的家伙再也回不来了 这种悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞和懊悔 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样 凪的周围
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不全是光芒在闪耀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你一直都低着头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连这种事都搞不清楚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪的身边不是有很多光芒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的 光芒…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的希望已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的光 至今还在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 虽然做了很多过分的蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想失去她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我很弱 即使这是个疯狂的地方 也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 会保护我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贫血? ?不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了 身体…麻痹了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:07:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 最后一次吃「Candy」是什么时候来着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 「猫头鹰」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我挺起腰杆啊 凪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我们的老大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那铃声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表我也有着重要的伙伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 唐子 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要哭要赎罪 等逃出这里后再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别泡我的修罗 你这混蛋女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别大呼小叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我难得让她得到了救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个想要见见自己孩子的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个一心想要帮助别人的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜 生 艹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 你会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不起作用?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧 想我救你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我避开了心脏和肺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过应该刺进骨头里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人深爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由你来把她送上西天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是她最好的救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没说错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是憎恨一切 用杀戮来救赎的修罗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不过是个软弱的人类罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死 怎会是救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的救赎 就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 为了自由而并肩作战的同伴就在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是认真的吧 「猫头鹰」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疯掉的你很美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀戮的身影也很迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾爱着你呦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要变回那个无法普度众生的混帐伪君子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就由我来将你救赎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊 弦角…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 弦角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布施的时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南无阿弥陀佛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又到镇上和人打架了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原以为你是个温驯稳重的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶因只会招致恶果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不恨他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个扭曲的现世上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懦弱地不幸地 陷于无上的愚蠢之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普度众生的方法是否存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻悟真的就能逃脱生老病死么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么佛祖大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不知道什么是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却认定死亡是痛苦的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 救救 我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,益信 午安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白 如何普度众生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静寂就是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平也是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安宁即是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执枉也是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善美都是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻悟也是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案就是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡才是救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又吉 晴美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都是挣扎着想逃出去的「Deadman」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能望着外界死去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多好的坟墓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒素蔓延 很痛苦吧 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地下就是你们的坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在恐惧中 僵化狂暴地活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身沾满了着罪和五脏六腑而死去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才能得到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我这个超级和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来赐予你们拯救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:31.49,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(729,645)}Grateful Dead
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚空一闪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:52.68,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(642,645)}Invisible Black
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点程度就裂开了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是很脆弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 他们必须被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 必须要哭泣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我 什么都做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快挂掉的可怜小猫还是做掉比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到被救赎之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直拯救下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐惧 压抑 背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝望 侮辱 后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤 痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疯狂 痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会从fucking的世界中拯救你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫的 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次 轮到我当Ace Man了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的大家都懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只要有朋友在 就有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁有闲工夫找死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起下地狱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我的救赎么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十岚 你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎 已经用不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然充满了希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖的雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会出现美丽的彩虹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 你不出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说过很想出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能丢下朋友不管的 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 之前打了你 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我 还做了过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 已经不痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还一起看到了闪闪轮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后有机会一起坐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 还有哪里痛么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是糖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这件事以后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 以后就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦角他们居然这么不顶用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸色很不好啊 创办人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是被死囚逃狱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 莳名小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的管辖区内没有少哪一个囚犯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是还不习惯当所长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没经过交接 他突然就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 我的管辖区内没有少人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5580号五十岚丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和9061号鹰见羊都回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都受了重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这11天里 他们去了哪里 干了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就去审问清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看情况也许会上点家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没你的风格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你喜欢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.72,0:22:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会听到趣事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.91,0:22:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要揉肩膀么 莳名长官
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人选定好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从创始人名簿上的一般犯人之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选出了一名最合适人选
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 要行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.05,0:22:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子果然很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有那么强的「罪之枝」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么味道的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做尽坏事的啄木鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.23,0:23:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也在不停地啄 森林已是千疮百孔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发怒了的森林之神 将它的喙变成了毒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦恼的啄木鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巢穴染上了毒 食物也染上了毒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友碰到它 全都相继地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤的啄木鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩有毒的泪水闪烁着光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.53,0:23:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.37,0:23:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.16,0:24:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是丸太的妈妈写的歌嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很怀念 但还是别唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.46,0:24:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.67,0:24:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候…红衣男也唱了这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.72,0:24:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.72,0:24:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那个家伙 为什么会知道这首歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
