Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.99,0:24:37.03,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}流星 black & night
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.08,0:24:40.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪止不住 一直流
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.70,0:24:49.13,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}恨 恨这不公的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.17,0:24:57.55,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这座迷宫 想逃 却没有出口
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.68,0:25:01.68,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追求自由的我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.64,0:25:10.86,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}倒立着 俯看天空
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.28,0:25:18.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我已经不是昨天的我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.08,0:25:25.62,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Shiny Shiny 夜空洒遍了星辉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.83,0:25:34.13,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}世界竟如此美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.38,0:25:41.06,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Shiny Shiny 月光载满了希望
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.06,0:25:49.06,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}世界是这般精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.06,0:25:51.73,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不是吗?
